name: Mobiacube

overview:
Mobiacube provides interactive mobile solutions and designs, develops and builds cutting edge applications and technologies for the mobile, digital and media markets.

Our team is composed by talented multimedia artists, skilled user experience designers, mobile and software developers in modern technologies (Cocoa, Android, GWT, Spring, HTML5, JS …).

Mobiacube focuses on five well defined platforms that have been developed specifically to encourage data use. These platforms are accepted globally and have the built in capabilities to allow for service innovation and include; iPhone, Android, Blackberry, Windows Mobile and Bada.

With an understanding of the mobile world and partners mobile, objectives Mobiacube has the flexibility to ensure business goals and objectives are aligned to the needs of each client and user group.
